OL,3,CFinance minister pushes ahead with
OL,4,Crate reform plan despite Executive
OL,5,Cshut out
OL,7,FThe Finance Minister has pressed ahead
OL,8,Fwith a public consultation on revenue
OL,9,Fraising reforms of the rates system,
OL,10,Fdespite failing to get the move
OL,11,Fendorsed by the wider Executive.
OL,13,FCaoimhe Archibald announced the
OL,14,Fconsultation plan in a statement to
OL,15,Fthe Assembly on Monday.
OL,17,FIt comes after she failed on four
OL,18,Foccasions across October and November
OL,19,Fto get it listed on the agenda of the
OL,20,FStormont Executive for discussion.
