OL,3,CFinance minister pushes ahead with
OL,4,Crate reform plan despite Executive
OL,5,Cshut out
OL,7,FThe plan includes raising the cap on
OL,8,Frates bills that applies to
OL,9,Fhouseholders living in more expensive
OL,10,Fhomes. The present cap applies to all
OL,11,Fhomes valued in excess of #400,000.
OL,12,FThe minister proposes to raise the
OL,13,Fvaluation at which the cap applies to
OL,14,F#485,000.
OL,16,FThere are currently 8,000 homes in
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland valued in excess of
OL,18,F#400,000 and raising the cap would
OL,19,Fgenerate an estimated extra #2 million
OL,20,Ffor the Executive each year.
