OL,7,FThe road-map for rates also proposes
OL,8,Fto reduce the discount for paying
OL,9,Frates bills early from 4% to 2%. In
OL,10,Fthe last financial year, more than
OL,11,F163,000 ratepayers availed of the 4%
OL,12,Fdiscount.
OL,14,FThe proposed reduction in the discount
OL,15,Fto 2% would generate a further #4
OL,16,Fmillion in annually recurring savings
OL,17,Ffor the Executive.
OL,19,FThe public consultation on those
OL,20,Fmeasures will now be launched in
OL,21,FJanuary.
