OL,7,FThe minister also announced a review
OL,8,Fof all current supports offered within
OL,9,Fthe rating system, initially looking
OL,10,Fat the Small Business Rate Relief
OL,11,FScheme and Non-Domestic Vacant Rating
OL,12,Fexclusions.
OL,14,FMs Archibald said her officials would
OL,15,Falso commence preparatory work on a
OL,16,Fnew domestic revaluation that would
OL,17,Fsee more than 800,000 residences
OL,18,Fassessed and revalued.
