OL,7,FWhile Ms Archibald did not formally
OL,8,Frequire Executive approval to launch
OL,9,Fthe public consultation, she will need
OL,10,Fthe support of other ministers if she
OL,11,Fintends to introduce any of the
OL,12,Fproposed measures once the consulting
OL,13,Fexercise is over.
OL,15,FMs Archibald outlined her proposals to
OL,16,Fthe Assembly on Monday.
