OL,7,F"Today kick starts a vital process of
OL,8,Fwork required to build a progressive
OL,9,Frates system based on the principles
OL,10,Fof fairness and equity, which aligns
OL,11,Fand underpins Executive priorities,
OL,12,Fstimulates our economy and supports
OL,13,Fthe growth of our taxbase by creating
OL,14,Fthe conditions for businesses to
OL,15,Fthrive," she said.
OL,17,F"The rating system is the Executive's
OL,18,Fmain lever to generate revenue and is
OL,19,Fcritical for the funding of our public
OL,20,Fservices, raising in the region of
OL,21,F#1.5 billion annually.
