OL,7,F"Rate relief provides important
OL,8,Fsupport to thousands of businesses and
OL,9,Fhouseholds. We must therefore ensure
OL,10,Fsupports are targeted towards those
OL,11,Fwho need it most or those who are
OL,12,Fvulnerable, and that any rate reliefs
OL,13,Fare meeting their policy objectives.
OL,14,FThe more revenue spent on rate
OL,15,Fsupport, the less there is for vital
OL,16,Fpublic services.
