OL,7,F"I am therefore committing to
OL,8,Freviewing every single rating support
OL,9,Fmeasure within a Strategic Review
OL,10,FCycle. To be clear review does not
OL,11,Fmean removal.
OL,13,F"The process I have announced is about
OL,14,Fensuring the support we have in place
OL,15,Fis achieving the desired policy
OL,16,Foutcome and using the resources we
OL,17,Fhave to best meet the needs of our
OL,18,Fcitizens and businesses."
